[src:trpc-typesafe/global-objects-promise] Note that the function `troubleWithGetNumber()` ends with a `throw`.
[src:trpc-typesafe/global-objects-promise] That is forced because a promise chain goes through all the `.then()` promises, even after an error, and without the `throw`, the error would seem "fixed".
